  in-process PatternMatcher (regex heuristics), which runs with zero latency and
  no external dependency. This adapter adds AI-layer depth.

  If this service is unreachable, the build emits DetectorUnavailableAlert (WARN)
  and continues — it does NOT block the build. The PatternMatcher already handled
